{"title_page": "Gossip Lanka News", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=September 2019}}\n{{multiple issues|\n{{more citations needed|date=January 2019}}\n{{one source|date=January 2019}}\n}}\n{{Infobox website\n| name = Gossip Lanka (Pvt) Ltd\n| logo = \n| logocaption = Underground News from Sri Lanka\n| screenshot = \n| collapsible = \n| collapsetext = \n| caption = \n| url = {{URL|www.gossiplanka.com}}\n\n {{URL|www.gossiplanka.info}}\n| commercial = \n| type = News Website\n| registration = Gossip Lanka (Pvt) Ltd\n| language = Sinhala\n| content_license = D.I.G. Athapaththu\n| author = Gossip Lanka\n| launch_date = <!-- {{Start date and age|2008|07|14|df=yes}} -->\n| alexa = {{DecreasePositive}} 6,112; 08: Sri Lanka ({{as of|2019|1|19|alt=January 2019}})<ref name=\"alexa\">{{cite web|url= http://www.alexa.com/siteinfo/gossiplanka.com |title= gossiplanka.com | publisher= [[Alexa Internet]] |accessdate= 19 January 2019 }}</ref><!--Updated monthly by Gossip Lanka (Pvt) Ltd.-->\n| revenue = \n| current_status = \n| footnotes = \n}}\n\n==[https://www.gossiplanka.com Introduction]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gossiplanka.com/|title=Gossip Lanka News|website=Gossip Lanka News|access-date=2020-02-06}}</ref>==\n'''Gossiplanka.com''' is a [[Sri Lanka]]n online news website containing Sri Lankan and world news written in [[Sinhala language|Sinhala]]. As of January 2019, [[Alexa Internet]] ranks its website traffic 8th in Sri Lanka, and in the low 7000s in the world.<ref name=\"alexa\"/>\n[https://www.gossip99.com Gossip] Lanka News launched on 14 July 2008, as a novel concept in Sri Lankan web sites. It was initially launched as a gossip Lanka blog\nSince its inception have become popular due to reports of hidden news and hidden stories in currant affair news and popular culture. When it's developing age interaction with readers with comments and it possible to have a lot of ideas and make a platform for public ideas.\n\n== Coverage ==\n[https://www.gossip99.com Gossip Lanka] News have covered all the controversial news of the past years in Sri Lanka, also covered publication of photographs, festivities, weddings etc.\nIt always been new because of the introduction of voice commands, photo dialogs, and many of other new features, from a periodical to the Web site. Also have a Facebook page, YouTube channel and a Twitter page.\n\n== Awards and achievements ==\n2013 [https://www.gossip99.com Gossip Lanka] has been nominated for the most popular website at the SLIM Nielsen Awards. It has been named as the most viewing web site ever in the world of Internet-based IT surveys.\n[https://www.gossiplanka.com Gossip Lanka], which ranked top out of the websites of local websites from February 2011 according to Alexa ranked websites, continued to stay to date.\nGossip Lanka was the brainchild of a number of other [https://www.gossip99.com Gossip] websites, and this was the key to maintaining [https://www.gossiplanka.com Gossip] websites, even in mainstream media.\n[https://www.gossip99.com Gossip Lanka News] is different from the one used by other Gossip websites and is the main streamlined and site-related web site responsible for reporting. As a result, the majority of them have been able to maintain their unwavering trust.\n\n==See also==\n* [[Electronic journalism]]\n* [[Internet radio]]\n* [[Internet television]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[https://www.gossiplanka.com English site]\n*[https://www.gossiplanka.com Sinhala Site]\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Gossiplanka.com}}\n[[Category:Asian news websites]]\n[[Category:Newsletters]]\n[[Category:Newspapers published in Sri Lanka]]\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=September 2019}}\n{{multiple issues|\n{{refimprove|date=January 2019}}\n{{one source|date=January 2019}}\n}}\n{{Infobox website\n| name = Gossip Lanka (Pvt) Ltd\n| logo = \n| logocaption = Underground News from Sri Lanka\n| screenshot = \n| collapsible = \n| collapsetext = \n| caption = \n| url = {{URL|www.gossiplanka.com}}<br>\n\n        {{URL|www.gossiplanka.info}}\n| commercial = \n| type = News Website\n| registration = Gossip Lanka (Pvt) Ltd\n| language = Sinhala\n| content_license = D.I.G. Athapaththu\n| author = Gossip Lanka\n| launch_date = <!-- {{Start date and age|2008|07|14|df=yes}} -->\n| alexa = {{DecreasePositive}} 6,112; 08: Sri Lanka ({{as of|2019|1|19|alt=January 2019}})<ref name=\"alexa\">{{cite web|url= http://www.alexa.com/siteinfo/gossiplanka.com |title= gossiplanka.com | publisher= [[Alexa Internet]] |accessdate= 19 January 2019 }}</ref><!--Updated monthly by Gossip Lanka (Pvt) Ltd.-->\n| revenue = \n| current_status = \n| footnotes = \n}}\n\n==[https://www.gossiplanka.com Introduction]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gossiplanka.com/|title=Gossip Lanka News|website=Gossip Lanka News|access-date=2020-02-06}}</ref>==\n'''Gossiplanka.com''' is a [[Sri Lanka]]n online news website containing Sri Lankan and world news written in [[Sinhala language|Sinhala]]. As of January 2019, [[Alexa Internet]] ranks its website traffic 8th in Sri Lanka, and in the low 7000s in the world.<ref name=\"alexa\"/>\n[https://www.gossip99.com Gossip] Lanka News launched on 14 July 2008, as a novel concept in Sri Lankan web sites. It was initially launched as a gossip Lanka blog\nSince its inception have become popular due to reports of hidden news and hidden stories in currant affair news and popular culture. When it's developing age interaction with readers with comments and it possible to have a lot of ideas and make a platform for public ideas.\n\n== Coverage ==\n[https://www.gossip99.com Gossip Lanka] News have covered all the controversial news of the past years in Sri Lanka, also covered publication of photographs, festivities, weddings etc.\nIt always been new because of the introduction of voice commands, photo dialogs, and many of other new features, from a periodical to the Web site. Also have a Facebook page,  YouTube channel and a Twitter page.\n\n== Awards and achievements ==\n2013 [https://www.gossip99.com Gossip Lanka] has been nominated for the most popular website at the SLIM Nielsen Awards. It has been named as the most viewing web site ever in the world of Internet based IT surveys.\n[https://www.gossiplanka.com Gossip Lanka], which ranked top out of the websites of local websites from February 2011 according to Alexa ranked websites, continued to stay to date.\nGossip Lanka was the brainchild of a number of other [https://www.gossip99.com Gossip] websites, and this was the key to maintaining [https://www.gossiplanka.com Gossip] websites, even in mainstream media.\n[https://www.gossip99.com Gossip Lanka News] is different from the one used by other Gossip websites and is the main streamlined and site-related web site responsible for reporting. As a result, the majority of them have been able to maintain their unwavering trust.\n\n==See also==\n* [[Electronic journalism]]\n* [[Internet radio]]\n* [[Internet television]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[https://www.gossiplanka.com English site]\n*[https://www.gossiplanka.com Sinhala Site]\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Gossiplanka.com}}\n[[Category:Asian news websites]]\n[[Category:Newsletters]]\n[[Category:Newspapers published in Sri Lanka]]\n", "name_user": "Jamesmcmahon0", "label": "safe", "comment": "clean up,typo(s) fixed: Internet based \u2192 Internet-based", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gossip_Lanka_News"}
